---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const updated = 'July 8, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms governing the use of evautopro.com and business inquiries made through it."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-14 lg:py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink-900 tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-700">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">1. About This Website</h2>
        <p>
          evautopro.com is operated by Shandong Wencai Import &amp; Export Co., Ltd.
          (山东稳彩进出口有限公司) ("EV Auto Pro", "we"). The website presents our vehicle export
          services to business buyers and allows you to send us inquiries. By using the site you
          accept these terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">2. Information, Not an Offer</h2>
        <p>
          Vehicle listings, specifications, availability figures and prices shown on this website are
          for general information only and do not constitute a binding offer. All sales are concluded
          through a separate written sales contract that states the final specification, price,
          delivery terms and payment terms. In case of any difference between website content and a
          signed contract, the contract prevails.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">3. Vehicle Specifications</h2>
        <p>
          Manufacturers may change specifications, equipment and appearance without notice. Driving
          range figures are measured under standard test cycles (such as CLTC or WLTP) and real-world
          results vary with conditions. Images are illustrative and may show optional equipment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">4. Buyer Responsibility for Import Compliance</h2>
        <p>
          Import regulations, homologation requirements, taxes and duties differ by country. Unless
          agreed otherwise in writing, the buyer is responsible for confirming that a vehicle may be
          imported and registered in the destination market. We provide export documentation from the
          Chinese side as described in our services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">5. Trademarks</h2>
        <p>
          Vehicle brand names and logos shown on this site belong to their respective manufacturers
          and are used to identify the products we supply. Their appearance does not imply endorsement
          of this website by the manufacturers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          We take care to keep website content accurate but do not guarantee that it is complete,
          current or error-free. To the extent permitted by law, we are not liable for losses arising
          from reliance on website content alone. This does not limit any liability agreed in a signed
          sales contract.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-2">7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms:
          <a href="mailto:cai@evautopro.com" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">cai@evautopro.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
